01:09:24.591 --> 01:09:28.761
And from the time
Pistachio was born

01:09:28.764 --> 01:09:31.430
to the first time
he took his first trot,

01:09:31.432 --> 01:09:34.166
your mom helped
Misty with him.

01:09:34.167 --> 01:09:36.171
