01:23:15.622 --> 01:23:17.656
Congratulations!

01:23:17.658 --> 01:23:19.157
Thank you.

01:23:19.159 --> 01:23:20.992
I knew you three
would be the perfect team.

01:23:20.994 --> 01:23:22.827
